<br />
<br />The gets small quickly, doesn't it?
<br />
<br />The easiest way I've found to silence the music is to just overwrite the music pointer addresses with ones that just point to a single FF byte, which typical indicate the end of a track. I've had to do this a few times in my projects. Sounds like that's what you're doing Mr. 8bit but I'm not sure..

		

		</td>
