	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'm going to have to pass on Punch Out!! - I was only successful for these three:
<br />
<br />01A530 (02) Title
<br />01A4EB (03) Intro Sequence
<br />01AD2E (1A) Password Screen
<br />
<br />00 is silence
<br />FF stops the music

		

		</td>
	</tr>
